<section id="scenarios-singleVO">
<title>Single VO/Multiple Resources</title>

<para>
In the situation where a single virtual
organization contains multiple resources and has administrative control over
those resources the configuration of the Inca components is simple. 
</para>

<para>
Scalability and reliability may still be issues if the VO has a large number
of resources or wishes to collect a large amount of data from the resources.
For these reasons the suggested arrangement includes multiple depots to handle
a heavy load and for fault tolerance.
</para>

